text: L'Étranger may refer to: ==Books== * "L'Étranger", a poem by Charles Baudelaire * The Stranger (Camus novel), a 1942 novel by Albert Camus * L'étranger series, a BL manga series by Kanna Kii ==Music== * L'Étranger (band), a 1980s Canadian punk band * "L'Étranger", a song (1934) by Édith Piaf * "L'étranger (voleur d'eau)", a 2018 song by Christine and the Queens * L'étranger, an opera by Vincent d'Indy
title: L'Étranger
